@@$TJvBlinkingLabel
<GROUP JVCL.LabelsAndStatic>
<TITLE TJvBlinkingLabel: overview>
  TJvBlinkingLabel extends the TJvLabel with options to let the label blink.

  To use a JvBlinkingLabel button
  * drop a TJvBlinkingLabel on a form.
  * Set Blinking to True to to let the label blink.
  * Set the property BlinkingDelay (in milliseconds) to determine the time the label is invisible
    during blinking.
  * Set the property BlinkingTime (in milliseconds) to determine the time the label is visible
    during blinking.
